<h3>GCBS Admission Instructions & Eligibility</h3>
<p><strong>Before applying</strong>, please read the instructions carefully and ensure you understand and meet the admission requirements.</p>

<h4>Who Can Apply?</h4>
<ul>
  <li>Students who have passed Class XII and meet the eligibility criteria. (<em>Check eligibility</em>)</li>
  <li>Applicants with a strong preference and commitment to completing a 4-year business program.</li>
</ul>

<h4>When to Apply?</h4>
<ul>
  <li>Explore the programs thoroughly before applying.</li>
  <li>Once sure of your eligibility and interest, click ‚ÄúAgree‚Äù and apply via the GCBS Admission Portal.</li>
  <li><strong>Last date for online registration: 15 March 2025</strong></li>
  <li>Applications are final once submitted; changes to program categories are not allowed.</li>
</ul>

<h4>Application Conditions</h4>
<p>Choose only <strong>one</strong> program category:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Category A:</strong> Bachelor of Accounting, Business Intelligence, or Finance & Economics.</li>
  <li><strong>Category B:</strong> Business Management, Human Capital Management, or Marketing (Digital & Communication).</li>
</ul>

<h4>Funding Options</h4>
<ul>
  <li>Higher-Education Grant (Government Scholarship)</li>
  <li>Self-Financed</li>
</ul>
<p>Ensure your personal details are accurate and your contact number remains active. You will receive a notification with your application number upon successful submission.</p>

